{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-464-mbius-function-and-intervals","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 464: Möbius funkcija i periodi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija Mobiusa, poznata kao $μ(n)$, definisana je na sledeći način:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$μ(n) = (-1)^{ω(n)}$ ako je $n$ bez kvadratnog faktora (gde je $\\omega(n)$ broj različitih primordnih delitelja za $n$)</li>\n<li>$μ(n) = 0$ ako nije $n$ bez kvadratnog faktora.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>$P(a, b)$ je broj cijelih brojeva $n$ u intervalu $[a, b]$ gdje je $\\mu(n) = 1$.</p>\n<p>$N(a, b)$ je broj celih brojeva $n$ u intervalu $[a, b]$ gde je $\\mu(n) = -1$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $P(2, 10) = 2$ i $N(2, 10) = 4$.</p>\n<p>Neka je $C(n)$ broj parova celih brojeva $(a, b)$ sa svojstvima:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$1 ≤ a ≤ b ≤ n$,</li>\n<li>$99 \\times N(a, b) ≤ 100 \\times P(a, b)$, na</li>\n<li>$99 \\times P(a, b) ≤ 100 \\times N(a, b)$.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Na primer, $C(10) = 13$, $C(500) = 16,676$ i $C(10,000) = 20,155,319$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $C(20,000,000)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f53d1000cf542c51004f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302139,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-464-mbius-function-and-intervals"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function mobiusFunctionAndIntervals() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nmobiusFunctionAndIntervals();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>mobiusFunctionAndIntervals()</code> trebalo bi vratit